@startuml gdsc-ys_mlops
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor "ML Developer" as Dev

rectangle "Client Application" as Client {
}

rectangle "Nginx" as Nginx #lightblue

rectangle "MLflow Server" as MLflow #palegreen

rectangle "MySQL" as MySQL #lightyellow

rectangle "AWS S3" as S3 #aliceblue

' ========== Connections ==========
Dev --> Client : Runs experiments\nLogs metrics\nRegisters models

Client --> Nginx : HTTP requests (REST API)\n- Track experiments\n- Log artifacts\n- Register models
Nginx --> MLflow : Proxy requests

MLflow --> MySQL : Store/retrieve metadata\n- Experiments\n- Runs\n- Models
MLflow --> S3 : Store/retrieve artifacts\n- Model files\n- Data snapshots\n- Visualizations

' Background processes
MLflow -> MLflow : Periodically syncs\nmetadata with MySQL
MLflow -> MLflow : Manages artifact\nlifecycle in S3
@enduml